## Disgust with Trump's racist, vulgar language

However, others paid more attention to the intent of Trump's words, rather
than how to translate them.

Prominent Japanese documentary filmmaker Soda Kazuhiro, in a tweet that was
shared hundreds of times, said that the â€œshitholeâ€ in question is inside
Trump's brain.

